sentences: Intars Busulis  (born 2 May 1978 in Talsi, Latvia) is a Latvian singer, trombonist and musician in a Musical Union Intars Busulis & Abonementa orķestris.
Wider recognition came from participation in a band called "Caffe", in 2001.
